Benefits reaped by each segments 
1>  Regular Consumers  and Food Chains - 
availability of exotic crops throughout the year at a cheaper rate than imported goods will increase sales and profit margins 

2>  Industries - 
Pharmaceuticals will get essential herbs to produce medicines conveniently moreover vertical farming enables us to supply our 
customers faster especially those who are away from agricultural regions, as Vertical Farms can be set up anywhere similar benefits
for beverage industries, also we aim to use plants as a tool where a vertical farm along the boundary of any factory ensures net 0 
carbon emission hence increasing goodwill of the company
